\f3\fs26 \cf0 Verify that my deployed expense agent is automatically registered in the Gemini\
Enterprise Agent Registry.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs24 \cf0 When Antigravity executes this prompt, it runs 
\f3\fs26 agents-cli publish gemini-enterprise --list
\f0\fs24  in the terminal. This queries the Agent Registry and lists all registered Gemini Enterprise agents in your project, allowing you to confirm that your Ambient Expense Agent is active and discoverable across your organization.\
